NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|On defense, think of yourself as a "bridge detective", Sherlock Holmes if you will. Drawing conclusions from the evidence presented. Many of the clues come from what is played and not played. But some of the clues (and this is what a lot of players forget) come from the bidding. |
