NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|This is a famous "negative inference", a conclusion you can draw by what was NOT bid. Just like the famous "dog that did not bark" clue in Sherlock Holmes. If you think of yourself as a bridge detective, and try to gather clues, it is amazing what you can figure out.|
