^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|When partner opens 1 of a minor, they virtually never have more than 4 in a major. Rarely they are 5-6 but you need not worry about that. You should assume, for the purposes of bidding that partner has no more than 4 of a major after opening 1@C or 1@D.|
